svg.title: kingscup
svg.text: Everyone chugs! You can stop when the person to your right stops, or just keep going. The person who picked the card get to stop first.

Everyone puts up their hands as if driving a car. The player who drew the card begins. Person A: *turns to left "Vroom" Person B: *turns to left "Vroom" Person C: *turns to right "Skert" Person B: *turns to right "Vroom"
Say a word, the person to the left of you have to say a word that rhymes with yours. Go around the room until someone fails.

The person who get this card is now Question Master. That means that if he/she ask a ques-tion and someone answers, that someone needs to drink. If some-one instead answers Fuck You, Question Master have to drink.

Pick a rule, usually something that you need to do every time you are supposed to drink. ex. A popular rule is to make it il-legal to say the word drink. Then every time someone says drink they must drink.Also pour some of your drink in the middle glass! The person to pick the last king chugs it.
Just the same as rhyme but with categories, for example cars: Volvo, BMW, Saab etc.
Play never have I ever with three fingers, take down a finger if you have done the statement. The person who take down all fingers first loses and drinks three times.
All the guys take a drink!
The person who draws a card puts their hands up towards the ceiling and the others should follow, last person in the group to do so loses and drinks.
If you break the circle of cards you have to down the middle cup.
Pick a drinking mate who will drink every time you drink.
If you picked this, give out two sips to a lucky someone!
Congratulations! You get to drink three sips.
